slides.content:
In `app.json`, add or modify the `icon` and `splash` fields:

```json
{
  "expo": {
    "name": "My App",
    "icon": "./assets/icon.png",
    "splash": {
      "image": "./assets/splash.png",
      "resizeMode": "contain",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff"
    },
    "ios": {
      "bundleIdentifier": "com.mycompany.myapp",
      "buildNumber": "1.0.0",
      "icon": "./assets/icon-ios.png"
    },
    "android": {
      "package": "com.mycompany.myapp",
      "versionCode": 1,
      "icon": "./assets/icon-android.png"
    }
  }
}
```

- Icons should be at least 1024x1024 (iOS) and 512x512 (Android).
- Splash screen images should match the device screen dimensions (Expo will scale).
